In "Advanced" go down to the recovery option and hit "e" to edit.
Go down to menuentry that includes "(recovery mode)"
Go to the line that starts with "linux" and add "init=/bin/bash" to the end of that line
CTRL/X to exit back to the "Advanced" menu select it and go.

